headline: JPMorgan’s Dimon wants Washington to 'look at all the rules and regulations' affecting big banks
summary: JPMorgan Chase CEO Jamie Dimon made it clear during a visit to the nation's capital Thursday that he is in favor of a restructuring of the financial regulatory agencies that oversee his bank and his industry.
